"'''Swoop Gangs'''" is a short story and article written by [[Wayne Humfleet]] and [[John Beyer]], originally published in [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 6|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 6]].

It was reprinted in ''[[Classic Adventures: Volume Four — The Best of the Journal]]''.

